Package: plotweave
Title: Weave ggplot2 Plots into HTML as SVG
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Joel", "Gsponer", , "joel.gsponer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tight control over converting ggplot2 plots to SVG with
    configurable fonts, dimensions, and styling. Enables embedding SVG plots
    in HTML tables (reactable and kableExtra), creating inline sparkline-like
    mini-plots powered by ggplot2, and arranging content in flexbox layouts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
