    cli,
    dplyr,
    forcats,
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.0),
    glue,
    htmltools,
    memoise,
    purrr,
    R6,
    rlang,
    stringr,
    svglite,
    tibble,
    vctrs
Suggests:
    ggdist,
    kableExtra,
    knitr,
    reactable,
    reactablefmtr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    tidyr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
